data.description: Welcome to this like-new, upgraded home in gated community featuring 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths with desirable open floor plan & natural light. Chef's Kitchen features an expanded island with Quartz Countertops, Beautiful Nutmeg Cabinets & upgraded appliances including 5-burner Gas Range with Lovely Overhead Hood & Touchscreen Oven. Spacious Great Room features upgraded beautiful Moscato laminate floors.  Upstairs spacious Primary Bedroom has a large walk-in closet & private Bath with double sinks & walk-in shower.  Additional features included upgraded carpet, designer paint & fixtures. For added energy efficiency & quiet soundproofing, residence contains Solar & added Whole House Insulation between floor & all interior walls. Prewired security system. Conveniently attached spacious 2-car Garage with utility sink. Property is located near neighborhood park & close to shopping & easy freeway access.  Welcome home!
